result.name: Grand Cuisine Shanghai Kitchen

reviews.text:
Typical Shanghaiese food is in Grand Cuisine Shanghai Kitchen.
You may have appetizers, soup, sea food, meat lover, vegetables, fried noodles, la main, dim sum, sweets, and drinks.
Good ambience,  but not so great service, staff not polite

A small shop serving Shanghainese cuisines. The standard of food is average but the fried pork dumplings is good. Reasonably priced but tried to avoid the peak lunch hours when you have to queue up for a table.

Good value afternoon tea 
Around$60 per person
食物水準大降....  the food used to be good, but so disappointed this time. The food was even well cooked

result.name: 君頤上海小廚

reviews.text: 擔擔麵的味道和口感都不錯👍
小🐉
2019年第一季裝修咗之後環境好咗。但係食物貴咗20個percent 。水準仍可保持。
十年如一日，水準沒變，很好吃。
我地今次叫左涼拌三拼：雞絲粉皮、涼拌小青瓜、夫妻肺片。同埋每次都必食既水煮牛肉，蒜香秋葵同孜然羊崧炒飯🤤炒飯超香，好正，水煮牛肉辣得好過癮🥰
